Package: pw3270
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: IBM 3270 Terminal emulator for gtk
 IBM 3270 terminal emulator gtk. It can be used to communicate with
 any IBM host that supports 3270-style connections over TELNET.

